Global Nintedanib API Market Insights
Nintedanib API Market size was valued at USD 0.70 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.15 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Nintedanib API Market Overview
The global Nintedanib API market is witnessing significant growth, driven by the rising demand for treatments in the therapeutic area of idiopathic pulmonary fibrosis (IPF) and other related lung diseases. The market size is expected to reach USD 3.2 billion by 2028, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 12% from 2023 to 2028. This surge is primarily attributed to the increasing adoption of Nintedanib as a primary treatment for IPF and other fibrosis-related conditions. The market is also benefiting from expanding research and development activities, coupled with favorable government initiatives supporting the growth of biologics and innovative therapies. The market's growth trajectory is further supported by the growing number of healthcare providers focusing on expanding their portfolios of generic and branded drug options.

